# GAIACOMCOIN (GCC) – LICENSE PROTOCOL

Version 1.2
Copyright © VisionGaiaTechnology

---

## 1. Overview

This repository uses a **layered licensing model**.

Core protocol infrastructure is open-source to ensure transparency,
auditability, and decentralization.

Governance and monetary control logic are protected to prevent
extraction, misuse, or hostile forks that undermine the protocol’s
ethical foundations.

---

## 2. Current License Scope (Present State)

The following existing modules are licensed under the **Apache License 2.0**:

* `/gcc_core`
* `/gcc_crypto`
* `/gcc_net`
* `/gcc_consensus`
* `/gcc_node`
* `/gcc_api`
* `/gcc_script`
* `/gcc_wasm`

These modules constitute **technical protocol infrastructure only**.

Apache License 2.0 grants:

* Free use, modification, and distribution
* Commercial use
* Explicit patent grant and patent retaliation protection

Full license text:
[https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0](https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0)

